 Soft Play 分享情感新单曲《Everything And Nothing》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-share-emotive-new-single-everything-and-nothing-listen-3762500?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=soft-play-share-emotive-新单曲一切皆无听Liberty DunworthTue, 04 Jun 2024 16:03:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3762500 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="软游戏，2024。" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是他们即将发行的专辑“Heavy Jelly”中分享的最新曲目</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-share-emotive-new-single-everything-and-nothing-listen-3762500">Soft Play 后分享的情感新单曲“Everything And Nothing”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="软游戏，2024。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Soft-Play@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-play">Soft Play</a> （前身为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slaves">Slaves</a> ）已经放弃了“Everything And Nothing”——他们即将发行的专辑中的最新单曲。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-on-their-name-change-and-new-music-we-can-be-aggressive-but-we-can-also-have-a-little-cuddle-3603130">软玩他们的更名和新音乐：“我们可以咄咄逼人，但我们也可以拥抱一下”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲于今天（6 月 4 日）分享，是继之前发行的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-fka-slaves-share-new-single-punks-dead-and-announce-surprise-reading-leeds-sets-3486125">Punk&#39;s Dead</a> 》、《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-hit-the-gym-for-heavy-new-single-mirror-muscles-3599751">Mirror Muscles</a> 》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-fka-slaves-share-brutal-single-act-violently-and-announce-new-album-heavy-jelly-3752887">《Act Violently》</a>之后，将与他们一起收录在他们即将发行的第四张录音室专辑《Heavy Jelly》中。它于 7 月 19 日发行，标志着他们以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slaves-announce-return-music-change-name-soft-play-3364247">新乐队名称</a>发行的第一张 LP，也是六年多来的第一个长篇项目。</p><p>在这首歌曲中，由艾萨克·霍尔曼 (Isaac Holman) 和劳里·文森特 (Laurie Vincent) 组成的乐队采取了比以往任何时候都更加激烈和开放的方式，远离了歌迷最常期望从他们身上听到的声音。</p><p>与前面提到的“Act Violently”不同，“Everything And Nothing”的歌曲感觉是由情感丰富的曼陀林和小提琴旋律支撑的。从本质上讲，霍尔曼从失去一位朋友中汲取灵感，并提出了两人罕见的脆弱感。</p><p>话虽这么说，乐队坚持认为这不是唱片上的象征性民谣，而是他们迄今为止最原始、最不妥协和最脆弱的作品。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="SOFT PLAY - 一切与虚无（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/a6IVRizF-iw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我在精神健康崩溃的最深处，开始在封锁中写下这些话。我的好朋友贝利刚刚去世，劳里不久也因癌症失去了他的伴侣艾玛，”霍尔曼谈到这首单曲的灵感时说道。</p><p> “这是一件事又一件事。我说到关于贝利的那句话，却想不起来接下来要说什么，所以我把它留在了原处。</p><p> “三年后（去年）我去了劳里家，他刚刚拿到了这把曼陀林，我们放下了乐器，我记得我手机上的笔记里有这些话，”他补充道。 “劳里问我这是什么意思，我很难解释，然后他说‘所以这就像一切，又什么都没有’。我们演示了这首曲子并将其带到录音室（歌词尚未完成）。在那段时间里，我不断看到看起来像贝利的人，这解锁了曲调的下一行，并让其余的内容出来。”</p><p>文森特补充道：“过去几年对很多人来说真的很艰难。歌曲和视频概括了我们所经历的旅程：失去、爱、重生，这是生命的循环。原始的痛苦和苦涩的美丽。”</p><p>这首歌还附有一段庆祝贝利一生的音乐视频。看看上面的内容。</p><p>专辑的实体格式包括 CD、黑色黑胶唱片、HMV 独家签名 CD 以及仅通过乐队官方商店和精选独立零售商出售的限量绿色黑胶唱片。您可以<a href="https://store.softplayband.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存专辑</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3752913" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752913" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752913" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="SoftPlay &#39;Heavy Jelly&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/SoftPlay-Heavy-Jelly-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3752913" class="wp-caption-text"> SoftPlay &#39;Heavy Jelly&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-on-their-name-change-and-new-music-we-can-be-aggressive-but-we-can-also-have-a-little-cuddle-3603130">Soft Play 向<em>NME</em>谈论了他们的更名事宜</a>，并透露，他们决定停用 Slaves 这个名字的部分原因是他们与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Bob-Vylan">Bob Vylan</a>歌手 Bobby 的一次谈话，因为人们认为这个名字对种族不敏感。</p><p> “他基本上说我们是他最喜欢的乐队之一，但他不会穿我们的商品，”霍尔曼解释道。 “如果他因为喜欢我们而感到不舒服，那么一定有其他人也有同样的感觉，”文森特说道。</p><p>乐队在声明中写道，他们之前“从恐惧和防御的角度回应了对这个名字的批评”，他们“害怕”如果改变这个名字会发生什么，因为他们的身份与这个名字有多么紧密的联系。姓名。文森特告诉<em>《NME》</em> ：“经过多年的治疗才克服这个问题。”</p><p>在其他消息中，二人组将于今年夏天进行一系列现场表演，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-lauren-mayberry-wunderhorse-lambrini-girls-lead-150-new-names-for-the-great-escape-2024-3597622">The Great Escape</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/download-2024-kerry-king-creeper-and-soft-play-lead-new-names-on-line-up-3610246">Download Festival</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-interview-bludfest-festival-milton-keynes-new-album-buy-tickets-3602830">Yungblud Fest</a> 。您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsoft-play-tickets%2Fartist%2F1871430" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问这里购买门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-share-emotive-new-single-everything-and-nothing-listen-3762500">Soft Play 后分享的情感新单曲“Everything And Nothing”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
