solo-headline-show-Machine-Gun-Kelly-live-guitarist.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="索菲·劳埃德 (Sophie Lloyd) 与机关枪凯利 (Machine Gun Kelly) 一起在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/SophieLloyd-debut-solo-headline-show-Machine-Gun-Kelly-live-guitarist.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/SophieLloyd-debut-solo-headline-show-Machine-Gun-Kelly-live-guitarist-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/SophieLloyd-debut-solo-headline-show-Machine-Gun-Kelly-live-guitarist-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/SophieLloyd-debut-solo-headline-show-Machine-Gun-Kelly-live-guitarist-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/SophieLloyd-debut-solo-headline-show-Machine-Gun-Kelly-live-guitarist-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/SophieLloyd-debut-solo-headline-show-Machine-Gun-Kelly-live-guitarist-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>网络红人、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/machine-gun-kelly">Machine Gun Kelly</a>的现场吉他手 Sophie Lloyd 宣布了她的首场个人头条秀。查找下面的所有详细信息。</p><p>这位音乐家去年 11 月通过 Autumn Records 发行了她的第一张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sophie-lloyd-guitar-internet-sensation-machine-gun-kelly-band-new-single-imposter-interview-3351615">“Imposter Syndrome”</a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sophie-lloyd-guitar-internet-sensation-machine-gun-kelly-band-new-single-imposter-interview-3351615">网络吉他红人索菲·劳埃德 (Sophie Lloyd) 谈论受《铁娘子》启发的单曲以及与机关枪凯利 (Machine Gun Kelly) 的巡演</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/youtube-guitar-sensation-sophie-lloyd-joins-machine-gun-kellys-live-band-3232645">她开始在 Machine Gun Kelly 的现场乐队中演奏，</a>参加 2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/machine-gun-kelly-announces-huge-us-uk-and-european-mainstream-sellout-tour-tickets-3186606">大型“Mainstream Sellout”世界巡演。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sophie-lloyd-guitar-internet-sensation-machine-gun-kelly-band-new-single-imposter-interview-3351615">当年，劳埃德在接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>称这次经历“令人惊叹”，并表示这是“一次旅程”。</p><p>今天（6 月 4 日），这位吉他手确认，她作为独奏者的“首次官方现场表演”将于 10 月 17 日星期四在伦敦北部的卡姆登集会场馆举行。</p><p>门票于本周五（6 月 7 日）上午 10 点（英国夏令时）开始公开发售 – <a href="https://myticket.co.uk/gigs/sophie-lloyd-london-2024-10-17-19-00" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里购买</a>。</p><p> “由于这是我的第一场演出，我想要一些比较私密的东西，所以数量非常有限，所以不要错过！”劳埃德在标题中写道。 “成为<a href="https://www.patreon.com/SophieGuitar" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Patreon 会员</a>后，您可以提前获得门票。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7ydbZoMmUl/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32